◆ cy_en_systick_clock_source_t

enum cy_en_systick_clock_source_t

SysTick clocks sources.

Enumerator
CY_SYSTICK_CLOCK_SOURCE_CLK_LF 

The low frequency clock clk_lf is selected.

CY_SYSTICK_CLOCK_SOURCE_CLK_IMO 

The internal main oscillator (IMO) clock clk_imo is selected.

CY_SYSTICK_CLOCK_SOURCE_CLK_ECO 

The external crystal oscillator (ECO) clock clk_eco is selected.

CY_SYSTICK_CLOCK_SOURCE_CLK_TIMER 

The SRSS clk_timer is selected.

CY_SYSTICK_CLOCK_SOURCE_CLK_CPU 

The CPU clock is selected.
